What is a class constructor?
a class constructor is a chunk or code that accesses a class outside of the class
i.e. calling upon the "item" class from my main game code

What should be included in a class constructor for orbs? Why?
the class name, the data you want to use in the class constructer
i.e. Orb(int x, int y){
}

What methods should the orb have? why?
Methods for things like hitboxes and what happens when this object touches 
this thing
